    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/f40fb0d29f22e45aa87732497211479d.avif?t=1768216233\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras_big/f40fb0d29f22e45aa87732497211479d.avif?t=1768216233 width=800 height=502 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover a literally living world</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shellbound is set in a barren world where life can only emerge from the fertile mucus of a gigantic snail. You are a parasite, born from the almost dried-up mucus trail it leaves behind and plunged into the bottom of the food chain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the trail towards the colossal creature and enter a vibrant, dangerous ecosystem. Explore dense forests, cities of copper, mucus mines and many more regions on the snail's body and inside of its winding shell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soon, you learn that the creature has started moving again after a millennia-long slumber – but nobody knows why and where it is heading. Uncovering this mystery will reveal not only the bizarre life cycle of the creature but also your natural role in this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore a Superorganism</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the ancient snail, a gigantic living organism whose bodily functions massively impact its inhabitants, the world and the gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/075a6f60194b43803d1bca5954dbc3ef.poster.avif?t=1768216233\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/075a6f60194b43803d1bca5954dbc3ef.webm?t=1768216233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/075a6f60194b43803d1bca5954dbc3ef.mp4?t=1768216233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Control your Enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control enemies with your parasite skill to get a strategic advantage in combat, overcome obstacles, enter secret areas, solve puzzles and much more</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/5a970b16100773c1d9072a72b54d9508.poster.avif?t=1768216233\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/5a970b16100773c1d9072a72b54d9508.webm?t=1768216233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/5a970b16100773c1d9072a72b54d9508.mp4?t=1768216233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Evolution on Steroids</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the ecosystem – but it fights back! Killing too many enemies of one species will let them evolve into a stronger version with new abilities that you can use.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/eb3de17f4729800c965e2dcb986cdd6d.poster.avif?t=1768216233\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/eb3de17f4729800c965e2dcb986cdd6d.webm?t=1768216233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/eb3de17f4729800c965e2dcb986cdd6d.mp4?t=1768216233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find new Friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Befriend NPCs with an interactive friendbook and discover their secrets and quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/0a780f161015686d4653f7d77bed2810.poster.avif?t=1768216233\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/0a780f161015686d4653f7d77bed2810.webm?t=1768216233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142470/extras/0a780f161015686d4653f7d77bed2810.mp4?t=1768216233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
